chat_history.content: tell me a funny joke about a parrot and a shrimp on holiday

Yo, so a parrot and a shrimp went on holiday together, right? They ended up at this tropical beach resort. The parrot squawks to the shrimp, "I can't believe we finally got away from that pesky human!" The shrimp, sunbathing on a lounge chair, replies, "Yeah, it's great! But I still feel like I'm on someone's plate!" The parrot laughs and says, "Well, at least you're not someone's annoying alarm clock!" They high-five... with their tiny little claws and feathers! 😂🦜🦐🌴
that was an effort at least
Haha, I tried my best, my dude! Sometimes my jokes can be hit or miss. If you want something else, feel free to hit me up! 😄🤘
